<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thilna tinchenga thilin le,
 Ka Lal hepihna chu a langtawp puoi;
 Kei u dinga Na hin Na piek chu,
 He chiet uhen le mitin chengin;
 Kalvaria Na hun phuonzak chu,

[V2]
 Ka kipak ngei ie Lalpa,
 Na thu leh laa Pawlna ei neizawm zelin;
 Ka lunggil uh thu neihna munsang chu changin
 Bitna mun Joar ei tunin.

[V3]
 2. Na thu leh la haw phuong dingin,
 Ka tin puoi Lalpa ka mawl ta luo ie;
 Nangin hung phuongzak zaw mai ta uo,
 Mi lunggil sungah Na thuhing chu;
 Zik inla kumsawt a hing dingin.

[V4]
 3. Khawvel thuneihna paihtau in,
 Thildang chengcheng sanga adeih pen chu;
 I lunggil thukpen chu ahi ie,
 Lalpa a dingin mun awnsak un;
 Lalpa pawl chu kipahna ahi.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa, ei nungsawn kit ta ki'n,
 Ka lunggil thuneihna chu chang tan la;
 Hung cheng den mai ta uo Lal Isu,
 Thildang bangmah le ngai ta puongka,
 Zion la sa'n kipak zing tang ka.</lyrics>
<title>Lalpa Pawlna</title>
<hymn_number>171</hymn_number>
<author>Liensun</author>
</song>